The paper discusses the use of Big Data in various fields such as science, engineering, economics, business, social science, and government, indicating a focus on data management and analysis (cs.DB). It also mentions the use of Big Data to boost organization performance, which involves information retrieval and machine learning techniques (cs.IR and cs.LG). The emergence of new technologies based on Big Data suggests a focus on cybersecurity (cs.CY) and cryptography (cs.CR).
